                      <b>Illinois Mathematics and Science Academy</b> on
                      <b>Wednesday, March 5th, 2025</b>. Teams will be in-charge
                      of their own transportation to and from the Illinois
                      Mathematics and Science Academy. Students should expect to
                      spend up to three hours on the contest.
                    </p>
                    <a
