                        >Virtual Competition</a
                      >
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                      The 35th Annual Junior High Math Contest's virtual
                      division will be held on
                      <b>Saturday, March 15th, 2025</b>. The contest is
                      currently scheduled from 9:00 AM to 9:00 PM in your
                      timezone, and students should expect to spend up to three
                      hours on the contest. Since the virtual contest will be
                      occuring at the international level, students will take
                      their tests asynchronously.
                    </p>
                    <a
                      href="https://forms.gle/Nyndsiz7H3dno7GK9"
